<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Our Hospital</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        header {
            background: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about, .services, footer {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            text-align: center;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #007bff;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Welcome to Our Hospital</h1>
        </header>
        <section class="about">
            <p>Our hospital is committed to providing the highest quality healthcare. Our experienced medical staff and modern facilities ensure that you receive the best care possible.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="services">
            <h2>Our Services</h2>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Specialties</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Internal Medicine</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Pediatrics</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Surgery</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </section>
        <footer>
            <p>If you have any questions or need a consultation, feel free to book an appointment with us!</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

